properties.Name: OccupationGroup
properties.Description:
A categorization of occupations related to consumer behavior as determined by individual's type of employment.

Ex:
-  Executive, Administrative, Managerial
-  Professional Specialty
-  Technician
-  Sales
-  Clerical
-  Private Household Service
-  Protective Service
-  Service Occupations Except Protective and Household
-  Farming, Forestry and Fishing
-  Precision Production, Craft and Repair
-  Machine Operators, Assemblers and Inspectors
-  Transportation/Material Moving
-  Handlers, Equipment Cleaners, Helpers, Laborers
